{"title":"口唱山歌心里甜","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":11,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"口唱山歌心里甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好年头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花果之乡好年头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树上树下两个秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树下谷穗沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树上苹果像皮球。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社化后水肥足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果乡年年闹丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北昌黎宋作人）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送公粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻谷迎风十里香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收喜讯传四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晒干风净谷粒壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员日夜送粮忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月当空晚风凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩挑公粮闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里乐来眼里亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收感谢共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东龚锦富）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薯堆山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山遍野银锄翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运薯队伍一线牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担叽咕歌声飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼地坝堆薯山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（重庆杨继武）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战“三秋”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田一弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水一弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近处红楼远处山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风物胜江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三秋激战竞争先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收在眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（重庆民歌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支山歌庆丰年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收田连丰收田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷穗结成黄金毯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面绣出诗一句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社万万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子多来歌也多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百担谷子万支歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上丘刚唱歌一首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下丘已打谷十箩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口唱山歌心里甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人喜庆丰收年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产跃进再跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活日日添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东民歌）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}